{"tid":1692143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護休班警,你我有責","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:31:57.000Z","uid":60916,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a3d9ee66b49b6c18cb943da61a352eddc27bbe","tid":1692143,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"屌哂你班連登仔咪搞同私了休班警啊<br />\n<br />\n平時串鳩人黑警咪算囉..咪搞休班警啦<br />\n嗰班正義既警察為左保護我地香港<br />\n幾個月日日正午時候著哂gear<br />\n熱到咁撚樣一陣中暑咁點算<br />\n仲要陪你地食Tear gas<br />\n仲要依家有屎魔法師<br />\n平時屌鳩人狗都算啦<br />\n<br />\n好心你地友唔好咁黑心啦<br />\n人地收工就搞休班警<br />\n一陣間唔小心打撚死左人點算<br />\n咁樣做會好大獲架全部手足都會出事<br />\n咪去宿舍搞人地既家庭啦<br />\n人地都有仔女<br />\n人地都有屋企人<br />\n<br />\n保護休班警,你我有責<br />\n老豆搵仔你好收手啦<br />\n咪再起d警察底"},{"pid":"a1403a92e47941d316e9613b27bffc41371a0ddd","tid":1692143,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"簡單一句，有春袋揸定唔揸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692056</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd3b42359663b2d4e7329be32c2f51f06ae36fa9","tid":1692143,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"起完都無人睇"},{"pid":"b9eee67b110b76a28d2045d4f1e5163fd6b22301","tid":1692143,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"唔好搞休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb4749844210eed654aa648ccc02db699b4636f","tid":1692143,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"d43290b86498d788349c8a89305a74b84124d5e5","tid":1692143,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb4749844210eed654aa648ccc02db699b4636f","tid":1692143,"uid":2